body_text:
I think this is due to actual nvidia libraries not being available during "docker build" time.
AFAIK, only stubs exist for cuda libraries when running docker build.
@flx42 (from NVIDIA) has more in depth information on this.

body:
I think this is due to actual nvidia libraries not being available during "docker build" time.
AFAIK, only stubs exist for cuda libraries when running docker build.
@flx42 (from NVIDIA) has more in depth information on this.
